	The sh(1) cannot handle some variable expansion, described
	in the manual: ${#var}, ${var#expr}, ${var##expr},
	${var%expr}, ${var%%expr}

How-To-Repeat: 
	echo ${#PATH}
	echo ${PATH#*:}
	echo ${PATH##*:}
	echo ${PATH%:*}
	echo ${PATH%%:*}
	All of them generate:
	Syntax error: Bad substitution
